      "content": "Hey, can you run a full review of the Q3 expense reports against our recent alpha performance? I need a breakdown of where our overhead is going and if any of our current resource allocations are looking inefficient. Just give me a summary of the main cost drivers and any red flags you see for the next quarter.",
